<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 18:07:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>2500万年前的一次突变如何让人类失去了尾巴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-03/ty-article/how-a-single-mutation-25-million-years-ago-cost-humans-our-tails/0000018e-04ec-d5dd-abce-cfee635e0000</link><description>一项新的研究探讨了人类尾巴缺失背后的神秘遗传机制，一些人认为这可能是类人猿两足行走的关键</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 18:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-03/ty-article/how-a-single-mutation-25-million-years-ago-cost-humans-our-tails/0000018e-04ec-d5dd-abce-cfee635e0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 149 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-149/0000018e-0558-d5dd-abce-cf7a9a0e0000</link><description>在卡塔尔称哈马斯未能发送待释放俘虏名单后，以色列坚持派代表团前往开罗 ■ 哈马斯消息人士称，协议可能“在几天内达成” ■ 以色列国防军：对超过 115 名等待援助的加沙人死亡的初步调查发现，以色列军队并未袭击他们 ■ 以色列国家粮食安全委员会主席因加沙“极度饥饿”而呼吁停火 ■ 战争已持续 149 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 17:45:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-149/0000018e-0558-d5dd-abce-cf7a9a0e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方没有意识到加沙地带因饥饿而造成大规模死亡的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/the-israeli-military-doesnt-grasp-the-risk-of-mass-death-by-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-041f-dc7c-a3cf-4cffa3aa0000</link><description>针对等待援助卡车的巴勒斯坦人的枪击事件反映出他们对局势严重性的无知。尽管以色列无视人道主义组织的警告，但世界正在倾听</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 17:19:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/the-israeli-military-doesnt-grasp-the-risk-of-mass-death-by-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-041f-dc7c-a3cf-4cffa3aa0000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔镇压巴勒斯坦标志，以色列警方逮捕挥舞巴勒斯坦国旗的足球迷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-soccer-fan-waving-palestinian-flag-amid-crackdown-on-palestinian-emblems/0000018e-04ff-d6be-afff-44ff85670000</link><description>尽管极右翼国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）努力使之成为非法行为，但在以色列，挥舞巴勒斯坦国旗并不是非法行为。据警方称，这名 18 岁粉丝在被释放前受到“严厉审问”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 16:48:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-soccer-fan-waving-palestinian-flag-amid-crackdown-on-palestinian-emblems/0000018e-04ff-d6be-afff-44ff85670000</guid></item><item><title>重新生活需要时间：以色列士兵在加沙预备役后适应生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/it-takes-time-to-live-again-israeli-soldiers-adjusting-to-life-after-gaza-reserve-duty/0000018e-049b-d6be-afff-44db8f030000</link><description>10月份，超过30万以色列人被征召入伍，其中许多人在战争中度过了前所未有的长时间远离家人的时光。三名战斗预备役军人讲述回国时“从100到0”的挑战</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 16:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/it-takes-time-to-live-again-israeli-soldiers-adjusting-to-life-after-gaza-reserve-duty/0000018e-049b-d6be-afff-44db8f030000</guid></item><item><title>他们购买了以色列的梦想之家。现在它们一文不值</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-bought-their-israeli-dream-homes-now-theyre-worth-nothing/0000018d-fad6-da4e-adbf-faff939e0000</link><description>10 月 7 日事件的以色列幸存者分散在全国各地，仍在为荒凉地区被毁的房屋支付抵押贷款。银行坚称价值下跌是暂时的</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 15:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-bought-their-israeli-dream-homes-now-theyre-worth-nothing/0000018d-fad6-da4e-adbf-faff939e0000</guid></item><item><title>“我的观点是贝都因人、巴勒斯坦人和山顶青年之间没有太大区别”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-thought-there-isnt-much-difference-between-bedouin-palestinians-and-hilltop-youth/0000018d-982d-d92c-a9ed-fbfdfaaa0000</link><description>以色列摄影师安妮·西敏·希特里特 (Anne Simin Shitrit) 放弃了宗教信仰，与定居者一起生活。在她的新展览中，她以您从未见过的方式展示了西岸青年</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 15:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-thought-there-isnt-much-difference-between-bedouin-palestinians-and-hilltop-youth/0000018d-982d-d92c-a9ed-fbfdfaaa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高粮食安全官员以加沙“极度”饥饿为由呼吁停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/citing-extreme-hunger-in-gaza-israels-top-food-security-official-calls-for-cease-fire/0000018e-048b-d6be-afff-44cbd45e0000</link><description>上届政府任命的粮食安全负责人罗尼·斯特里尔教授警告说，以色列是国际协议的缔约国，这些协议要求以色列保护战区平民的生命并遵守“明确的游戏规则”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 14:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/citing-extreme-hunger-in-gaza-israels-top-food-security-official-calls-for-cease-fire/0000018e-048b-d6be-afff-44cbd45e0000</guid></item><item><title>美国通过甘茨邀请向内塔尼亚胡发出明确信息——无论拜登是否承认</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sends-clear-message-to-netanyahu-with-gantz-invite-whether-biden-admits-it-or-not/0000018e-0431-ded4-a3ee-df3d64ad0000</link><description>战时内阁部长本尼·甘茨访问华盛顿会见副总统卡马拉·哈里斯和其他人，这表明白宫认为他，而不是总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡，才是耶路撒冷房间里的成年人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 14:10:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sends-clear-message-to-netanyahu-with-gantz-invite-whether-biden-admits-it-or-not/0000018e-0431-ded4-a3ee-df3d64ad0000</guid></item><item><title>报告发现，自 10 月 7 日以来，近 20,000 名以色列儿童被列为恐怖活动受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-report-finds-almost-20-thousand-children-classified-victims-of-terror-since-oct-7/0000018e-044f-d5c1-a98e-d44f02ee0000</link><description>以色列国家儿童委员会的新报告揭示了哈马斯大屠杀和随后的加沙战争对以色列儿童心理影响的程度，以及教育系统在应对方面如何准备不足</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 13:47:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-report-finds-almost-20-thousand-children-classified-victims-of-terror-since-oct-7/0000018e-044f-d5c1-a98e-d44f02ee0000</guid></item><item><title>连续多雨天气后，数百只异常巨大的水母被冲上以色列海岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-unusually-large-jellyfish-wash-up-on-israels-shores-after-spate-of-rain/0000018e-03cf-def2-a98e-cfff35c00000</link><description>虽然夏季通常被认为是水母的高峰季节，但冬季水母并没有什么异常，而且往往体型更大——尽管海洋专家表示，今年“它们的巨大体型”令人“难以置信”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 12:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-unusually-large-jellyfish-wash-up-on-israels-shores-after-spate-of-rain/0000018e-03cf-def2-a98e-cfff35c00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科技大亨称内塔尼亚胡副部长向部长施压，要求他放弃获得以色列奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-tech-mogul-says-netanyahu-associate-pressured-knesset-to-renege-his-israel-prize/0000018e-040f-d12c-a3bf-ffcf14110000</link><description>在以色列议会委员会听证会上，科技巨头埃亚尔·瓦尔德曼（Eyal Waldman）在诺瓦音乐节大屠杀中失去了他的女儿，他在以色列议会委员会听证会上流着泪声称，内塔尼亚胡的一位亲密关系人游说取消了他对以色列创业奖的评选，并要求进行调查</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 12:27:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-tech-mogul-says-netanyahu-associate-pressured-knesset-to-renege-his-israel-prize/0000018e-040f-d12c-a3bf-ffcf14110000</guid></item><item><title>加沙成为以色列军用机器人试验场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gaza-becomes-israels-testing-ground-for-remote-control-military-robots/0000018e-03ed-def2-a98e-cfff1e640000</link><description>以色列在加沙增加使用机器人，可以在不危及士兵和狗生命的情况下进行初步监视</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 11:55:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gaza-becomes-israels-testing-ground-for-remote-control-military-robots/0000018e-03ed-def2-a98e-cfff1e640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列应赫尔佐格总统的要求修改欧洲歌唱大赛的歌名和歌词</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-eurovision-lyrics-to-be-revised-at-the-behest-of-president-herzog/0000018e-03b1-da4e-adbf-83b9c49c0000</link><description>代表以色列参加欧洲歌唱大赛的歌曲《飓风》是原曲《十月雨》的更新版，欧洲广播联盟因这首歌过于政治化而拒绝了这首歌</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 10:31:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-eurovision-lyrics-to-be-revised-at-the-behest-of-president-herzog/0000018e-03b1-da4e-adbf-83b9c49c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部女子被发现死在车内，其伴侣因涉嫌谋杀被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/woman-found-dead-in-car-in-north-israel-partner-arrested-on-suspicion-of-her-murder/0000018e-0360-d4e1-abce-0b65ce020000</link><description>警方称，该女子的伴侣是阿拉伯以色列城市什法阿姆的 58 岁居民，他已到警察局自首，称自己刺伤了妻子</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 08:30:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/woman-found-dead-in-car-in-north-israel-partner-arrested-on-suspicion-of-her-murder/0000018e-0360-d4e1-abce-0b65ce020000</guid></item><item><title>美国向加沙空运援助物资反映出拜登对以色列的失望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-aid-airlift-into-gaza-reflects-bidens-frustration-with-israel/0000018e-00e5-dd6a-a18f-eafd821a0000</link><description>由于哈马斯认为国际社会对以色列的批评使力量平衡向对其有利的方向倾斜，而内塔尼亚胡避免讨论第二天在加沙的计划，美国政府对以色列越来越不耐烦，并利用甘茨向总理施压</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 04:24:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-aid-airlift-into-gaza-reflects-bidens-frustration-with-israel/0000018e-00e5-dd6a-a18f-eafd821a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军任命了在加沙战斗中丧生的预备役军人；卡塔尔称哈马斯未提供人质名单后，以色列拒绝派代表团前往开罗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-live/hamas-expected-to-respond-to-hostage-deal-proposal-at-cairo-talks/0000018e-0223-d4e1-abce-0b27257d0000</link><description>哈马斯向阿拉伯媒体透露：停火协议可在“几天之内”达成 ■ 以色列国防军对加沙援助车队死亡情况的审查发现大多数死于踩踏事件 ■ 哈马斯卫生部表示，加沙至少有 15 名儿童死于营养不良和脱水医院 ■ 以色列国防军称，在对汗尤尼斯的军队袭击中，数十个哈马斯大院和基础设施被毁</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 03:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article-live/hamas-expected-to-respond-to-hostage-deal-proposal-at-cairo-talks/0000018e-0223-d4e1-abce-0b27257d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方将巴勒斯坦囚犯关押在临时笼状牢房中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-are-holding-palestinian-prisoners-in-makeshift-cage-like-cells/0000018e-00ea-da4e-adbf-82fb03180000</link><description>囚犯被关押在未经批准作为拘留设施的监狱设施中。耶路撒冷治安法院法官称这些条件“不适合人类”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 00:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-are-holding-palestinian-prisoners-in-makeshift-cage-like-cells/0000018e-00ea-da4e-adbf-82fb03180000</guid></item><item><title>“无法容忍的行为”：以色列国家安全委员会抵制本-格维尔会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-security-council-halts-sending-representatives-to-meet-minister-ben-gvir/0000018e-00a6-da4e-adbf-82bf45e20000</link><description>与以色列辛贝特安全部门一样，国家安全委员会停止派代表参加每周的会议，原因是担心本-格维尔部长及其同事使用手机，有时会非法拍摄机密与会者</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 20:29:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-security-council-halts-sending-representatives-to-meet-minister-ben-gvir/0000018e-00a6-da4e-adbf-82bf45e20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周五在汗尤尼斯爆炸中丧生的三名士兵的名字； 14人受伤，其中5人伤势严重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-khan-yunis-blast-on-friday-14-wounded-five-severely/0000018e-00bd-d4e1-abce-09bdd66e0000</link><description>被杀的三人是中士。多列夫·马尔卡，19 岁，中士。 Afik Tery，19 岁，中士。伊农·伊扎克，20</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 20:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-khan-yunis-blast-on-friday-14-wounded-five-severely/0000018e-00bd-d4e1-abce-09bdd66e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>